  "businessLogic": [
    "Read AccountDTO from the ACCOUNT_IDENTITY slot (DOMAIN.REQUEST).",
    "If AccountDTO is null, skip party fetch and return early.",
    "Collect all CollectionManagementParametersDTO items from interest, fee, and closure settlement preferences that have a non-blank counterPartyNumber, grouped by counterPartyNumber.",
